Built following:
https://realpython.com/build-a-chatbot-python-chatterbot/

To start
-------------------
create and activate a virtual environment, then install chatterbot and pytz:
PS> python -m venv venv
PS> venv\Scripts\activate
(venv) PS> python -m pip install chatterbot==1.0.4 pytz

During the first run, ChatterBot creates a SQLite database file where it stores all inputs and
connects them with possible responses.